they could set. The traps would be specific to the room type:
A thief would have maybe one or two traps for an outdoor city area, 
or an indoor city area, maybe another specifically for an alley (the most deadly)
 
whilst the ranger would have a list of traps, maybe just one for each wilderness room type.
A special trap for forests, and another for swamps, one for mountains,
maybe one for caves, or hill or desert. Whatever.
 
When the trap was chosen, via the craft skill (lets say one of the thieves
